snippet.title: Curse of the Catacombs gameplay (PC Game, 1993)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Curse of the Catacombs, Dos PC game produced by Froggman in 1993 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/curse-of-the-catacombs/8445/
Curse of the Catacombs is a first-person shooter very interesting. You're a mage whose quest is to destroy the evil Nemesis.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
